    <h1>Our Core Framework</h1>
    <p>Architecting contemporary custom structures and elite structural transformations across the Greater Tampa Bay
      area.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="story-section section-spacing">
  <div class="container story-grid">

    <div class="image-stack">
      <div class="frame-main">
        <img src="/images/livingroom.webp"
          alt="Open-concept custom luxury living room design layout featuring premium flooring and expansive window systems">
      </div>
      <div class="frame-sub">
        <img src="/images/bathroom.webp" alt="Bathroom detail showcasing clean lines and luxury finishes">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="story-text">
      <span class="meta-tag">The Blueprint</span>
      <h2>Rooted in Brandon. Engineered for Florida.</h2>
      <p>Founded originally in Brandon, Florida, <strong>Building Home</strong> was established to bridge the gap
        between progressive, high-end contemporary design aesthetics and the strict engineering requirements necessary
        for Gulf Coast survival.</p>
      <p>We approach construction through a highly disciplined grid layout system—maximizing natural light vectors while
        deploying heavy-gauge wind-resistant framing packages. Whether managing a sleek modern urban update along the
        coastal roads of Clearwater or pouring a monolithic foundation for an expansive custom build out in Wesley
        Chapel, our execution metrics never waver.</p>
      <p>Our operation respects local ecosystems, utilizing premium components, energy-efficient building wraps, and
        non-toxic materials engineered to thrive inside volatile climates.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

